cs.LO, cs.CR, cs.PL, cs.AI, cs.SE

Reasoning: 
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is the most likely category as the paper proposes a new temporal logic for reasoning about probabilistic hyperproperties and investigates statistical model checking algorithms for it. 
- cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is also likely as the paper shows how the proposed logic can express important probabilistic information-flow security policies. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is another possible category as the paper deals with temporal logic and its extensions. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is a possible category as statistical model checking is a technique used in AI for verifying properties of systems. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is also a possible category as the paper deals with verifying properties of systems using temporal logic and statistical model checking.
